WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:05.561
Hey, good morning, family. Praise the Lord. I'm glad you all joined me again today to pray.

00:00:05.562 --> 00:00:15.319
We have a lot of work to do, but I just want to give you all a testimony real quick about a lady who asked for prayer.

00:00:15.320 --> 00:00:32.983
She reached out to us and said she broke four ribs. I prayed for her on this video, and she was in a lot of pain with a broken hip and ribs. It was very painful for her.

00:00:32.984 --> 00:00:48.045
She contacted us and said, "When you were praying and believing for my healing, I just want to let you know the Lord healed me."I just want to give all the glory, honor, and praise to the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:00:48.046 --> 00:00:57.023
He is the Healer, healing the sick the same yesterday, today, and forever. He is a good God and a Healer.

00:00:57.024 --> 00:01:08.684
That’s why I have this shirt here; I want this to stand bold in black and white: "Jesus the Healer."He is a Healer and he is still healing the sick today.

00:01:08.685 --> 00:01:21.478
I’m bold about it because I've seen it time and time again. We are healed; we have to take it by faith.

00:01:21.479 --> 00:01:27.812
You’ve got to reach out and grab the hem of His garment by faith and call those things that be not as though they were.

00:01:27.813 --> 00:01:37.669
I’m excited about that. I just wanted to give God praise and a testimony that He is doing miracles through this YouTube channel.

00:01:37.670 --> 00:01:48.758
I’m believing for your manifestation. There’s a gentleman named Keith R whose last name starts with an R for privacy's sake.

00:01:48.759 --> 00:01:58.804
He writes us well-written letters that bless me every single time.

00:01:58.805 --> 00:02:08.481
He’s just so awesome the way he talks about his family and what he’s going through.

00:02:08.482 --> 00:02:12.584
He’s an elderly gentleman, but we look forward to him writing to us.

00:02:12.585 --> 00:02:18.802
We’ve kept every single letter; they are very precious to us.

00:02:18.803 --> 00:02:26.355
He is asking for his children to come home to the Lord. They are very liberal and need a touch.

00:02:26.356 --> 00:02:47.462
I’m going to believe God with him today. I felt the cry for the children to come home in the letter, and it really moved me today.

00:02:47.463 --> 00:02:57.116
The Lord was showing me there are so many of you with wayward children.

00:02:57.117 --> 00:03:09.836
You feel like you're at the end of your rope sometimes, feeling there's no hope because they are so lost.

00:03:09.837 --> 00:03:18.839
When you're at the end of the rope, Jesus has grabbed onto the rope with you. When all else is left to do, stand therefore.

00:03:18.840 --> 00:03:28.702
I want to encourage every one of you: do not give up on your unsaved loved ones.

00:03:28.703 --> 00:03:58.101
When I had my visitation over two weeks ago, the Lord told me, "You must pray for the blinders to come off their eyes and that the eyes of their understanding would be enlightened,"for Satan blinds the eyes of the unbeliever so they can't see the light of the truth.

00:03:58.102 --> 00:04:03.688
The Bible says to train up a child in the way they should go, and when they get older, they will not depart from it.

00:04:03.689 --> 00:04:10.432
Regardless of whether they are wayward, they are going to come back because those seeds of truth are planted inside of them.

00:04:10.433 --> 00:04:23.211
It doesn't matter if you feel you never trained them up; God is merciful and we can turn them around by prayer.

00:04:23.212 --> 00:04:36.117
First, it was on my heart to pray for the nation. We've seen some good fruit in the media.

00:04:36.118 --> 00:04:48.067
If my people who are called by my name will humble themselves and pray and turn from their wicked ways—look at what's happening. We see prayer groups and churches.

00:04:48.067 --> 00:05:05.214
Even with praying over President Trump, JD Vance came out and said, "Jesus is Lord."That’s a big statement for a politician to declare behind the podium.

00:05:05.214 --> 00:05:18.157
He said he got baptized; he even said it in 2019. To God be the glory for him being so bold about his faith.

00:05:18.158 --> 00:05:27.334
Keep on keeping on; we can't give up now. When you have momentum in the spirit realm, that’s when you push harder.

00:05:27.335 --> 00:05:39.275
You’ve got to make that devil a roadkill spot. It's like hitting an old roadkill; you keep grinding it down into the concrete.

00:05:39.276 --> 00:05:48.085
We keep knocking him in the head until he gets tired and goes away for a season. We have that kind of authority.

00:05:48.086 --> 00:05:55.179
The same Jesus Christ of Nazareth who was raised 2,000 years ago dwells on the inside of you.

00:05:55.180 --> 00:06:13.208
He is no respecter of persons. The same Jesus that lives in me lives in you.

00:06:13.209 --> 00:06:25.198
We have authority over the devil because the Bible tells us we do. We cannot just pray a weak, anemic prayer.

00:06:25.199 --> 00:06:41.030
It’s time we get bold about our faith and know that all things are possible to him who believes.

00:06:41.031 --> 00:07:00.466
Greater is He that is in you than he that is in the world. I’m using Keith R's children as a point of contact for every one of you.

00:07:00.467 --> 00:07:41.239
There’s power in taking the care out of your prayer. Take your eyes off the problem and look at Jesus because He is the answer.

00:07:41.240 --> 00:08:03.027
He has America, Australia, Canada, and Asia. We will see the greatest outpouring of the Spirit of God this world has yet seen.

00:08:03.028 --> 00:08:14.078
Father, we thank You for Keith R's children and we call all these children in right now in the name of Jesus.

00:08:14.079 --> 00:08:37.335
Satan, take your hands off our children and their eyes. We say they are saved, filled with the Holy Ghost, and on fire for Jesus.

00:08:37.336 --> 00:08:51.039
They are no longer wayward; they are coming home. This is the time for them to get radically born again.

00:08:51.040 --> 00:09:22.806
Father, we stand in the gap interceding for them. Angels, go on behalf of each person with wayward children.

00:09:22.807 --> 00:09:30.285
We call forth results. It will be first the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation.

00:09:30.286 --> 00:09:47.673
It’s time for a great acceleration. Every person represented here today, their children are wayward no more.

00:09:47.674 --> 00:10:05.867
We say they are saved and filled with the Holy Ghost. We take authority over the blinders over the unbelievers'eyes.

00:10:05.868 --> 00:10:31.239
We call in the Lord of the Harvest to bring in those children, relatives, husbands, or wives.

00:10:31.240 --> 00:10:37.601
We call for the hardness of their hearts to be soft to the gospel.

00:10:37.601 --> 00:11:12.116
We thank You, Lord, that they are calling today to say, "I am coming home; I want to be born again."I stand in agreement with every one of you.

00:11:12.117 --> 00:11:24.559
Father, we take communion over it. You are a Healer and a Deliverer.

00:11:24.560 --> 00:11:32.716
Bring those family members home because their eyes are open to the error of their ways.

00:11:32.717 --> 00:11:41.624
They don't want to go to hell; they are having an inward experience with the Holy Spirit to wake them up.

00:11:41.625 --> 00:12:09.168
We believe by faith that our children are coming home. We are healed and whole.

00:12:09.169 --> 00:12:18.091
No viruses will come nigh us this winter—no flu, no pestilence, no plagues, no nothing comes nigh us; Father, we walk in divine health.

00:12:18.092 --> 00:12:41.660
No respiratory infections; we call our bodies healed. For You were wounded for our transgressions and by Your stripes we are healed.

00:12:41.661 --> 00:12:46.926
I call forth new hearts, even for Sherry. Sherry needs a new heart.

00:12:46.927 --> 00:12:51.497
We thank You for a creative miracle in Sherry's heart, even with that pacemaker.

00:12:51.498 --> 00:13:07.099
We speak to that heart: be healed in the name of Jesus. No more fear or torment over you.

00:13:07.100 --> 00:13:18.308
We take authority over that demonic spirit and command it to go now.

00:13:18.309 --> 00:13:38.735
Fill your mind and spirit with God's word and meditate on it like medicine.

00:13:38.736 --> 00:13:44.007
Let it become rhema in your spirit. The heart is related to fear. Meditate on the word, for the truth will set you free.

00:13:44.008 --> 00:14:09.198
Get your heart lined up with the word, for the Bible says that men's hearts will fail them for fear.

00:14:09.199 --> 00:14:37.668
You've got to get fear out, for fear tolerated is faith contaminated.

00:14:37.669 --> 00:14:53.791
It may take having less time on social media or YouTube and getting the word inside because His words are life and health to all flesh.

00:14:53.792 --> 00:15:09.485
Sherry, turn the ship around because the Lord still has work for you to do.

00:15:09.486 --> 00:15:32.686
Do not have fear about what is coming upon the earth. Spend time with Him.

00:15:32.687 --> 00:15:37.618
Father, I thank You for the Covenant. Your promises are yes and amen.

00:15:37.619 --> 00:15:43.293
I call forth healing over these bodies, hearts, and minds. We take this body right now in Jesus'name.

00:15:43.294 --> 00:15:49.803
Lord, we thank You for the blood. If we make much of the blood, the blood will make much of us.

00:15:49.804 --> 00:15:55.383
We take the care out of our prayer. We confidently trust in the finished work of Jesus Christ.

00:15:55.384 --> 00:16:02.823
We call their eyes to be open. For Keith R's children and all those we stand in the gap for, we thank You, Father.

00:16:02.824 --> 00:16:10.263
This will be the greatest miracle-working year. Even before Thanksgiving, before November 27th, I believe there will be peace in the home with joy.

00:16:10.264 --> 00:16:16.153
It will be a time of Heaven on Earth in your homes. Having peace in the home is everything.

00:16:16.154 --> 00:16:19.873
I believe this will be the greatest holiday season you've ever had.

00:16:19.874 --> 00:16:22.973
We apply the blood over your children, husbands, and wives.

00:16:22.974 --> 00:16:30.413
We apply the blood over people tormented in the mind with depression or satanic bondage. We renew our minds with the word of God.

00:16:30.414 --> 00:16:36.613
When the waves and winds of life come and your house is planted upon the Rock, your house will stand.

00:16:36.614 --> 00:16:42.503
You’ve got to have your faith planted in the Lord Jesus Christ. The word will set the captives free.

00:16:42.504 --> 00:16:46.533
You can't stay free without the word of God down inside your heart.

00:16:46.534 --> 00:16:51.803
Listen to preachers like Brother Hagin or John Kilpatrick, but you must have the word in you.

00:16:51.804 --> 00:16:56.453
I knew I wasn't going to preach today, but it’s coming out of my spirit.

00:16:56.454 --> 00:17:02.343
You’ve got to get angry at the devil. You can't be passive about a devil trying to kill you.

00:17:02.344 --> 00:17:08.233
If you give him an inch, he'll take a mile. Jesus is coming; get your lamps filled with oil.

00:17:08.234 --> 00:17:13.193
I take this blood and apply it over our children. I anoint my children with oil.

00:17:13.194 --> 00:17:17.843
This represents the blood of Jesus. I'm wall-to-wall Holy Ghost and on fire for Jesus.

00:17:17.844 --> 00:17:23.113
I anoint my children before they go to school. I plead the blood of Jesus over you.

00:17:23.114 --> 00:17:28.693
I anoint their bodies. No sickness or virus comes in your nose at school; my house is covered.

00:17:28.694 --> 00:17:33.653
I anoint the back of their neck and their head; they have the mind of Christ.

00:17:33.654 --> 00:17:38.613
I prayed over Megan, and she is getting better and better. I see the fruit there.

00:17:38.614 --> 00:17:45.433
She is turning around, and I give God glory for it. One day she will come on here and give her testimony.

00:17:45.434 --> 00:17:51.633
She will be viral, showing that Jesus is the Healer to those who believe. Jesus is faithful. Anoint your bedposts.

00:17:51.634 --> 00:17:58.763
If you have a spouse who is a rascal or in sin, anoint them with oil and pray over them in their sleep.

00:17:58.764 --> 00:18:03.103
Anoint their pillow and headboard. Apply the blood over your car, doorposts, and windows.

00:18:03.104 --> 00:18:07.443
When you make much of the blood, the blood will make much of you.

00:18:07.444 --> 00:18:10.853
No calamity shall come nigh you. Father, we believe for America.

00:18:10.854 --> 00:18:16.123
It's on my heart to keep praying for Donald Trump and for all corruption to be uncovered.

00:18:16.124 --> 00:18:20.773
Only an awakening unto God will save America, but I believe You put Donald J.

00:18:20.774 --> 00:18:25.423
Trump in this position to lead us. I pray for supernatural wisdom over his mind.

00:18:25.424 --> 00:18:30.693
I speak boldness about his faith. Father, appear before him and shake him in the midnight hour.

00:18:30.694 --> 00:18:38.133
Call him to his knees for such a time as this. I thank You for a move of Your presence in the White House.

00:18:38.134 --> 00:18:41.543
JD Vance and all the cabinet members—we receive this by faith.

00:18:41.544 --> 00:18:45.883
Anyone who decrees that Jesus is Lord from a political platform is a shoo-in.

00:18:45.884 --> 00:18:54.253
I thank You that the people of God would rise up and vote righteously, not moved by gender, race, or color of skin, but by biblical principles.

00:18:54.254 --> 00:18:58.593
We vote for what You call godly. You are the pilot of our ship.

00:18:58.594 --> 00:19:02.003
Father, I thank You that President Trump is who You've picked.

00:19:02.004 --> 00:19:06.963
Anoint him and appoint him. We ask You to remove the evil people coming against him.

00:19:06.964 --> 00:19:07.163
We speak a shaking in the Democratic party and an exposing of all darkness. We call forth righteousness and truth.

00:19:07.164 --> 00:19:07.263
Let the blinders on every race's eyes be removed concerning their voting for Kamala Harris.

00:19:07.264 --> 00:19:07.363
I call for an exposing of this so they would come to their senses.

00:19:07.364 --> 00:19:07.463
Even people who are not believers would say, "What am I doing?

00:19:07.464 --> 00:19:07.663
They are ruining our country."We call for a supernatural turn of events in the polls. We are moved by what the word says.

00:19:07.664 --> 00:19:07.763
We call forth a red tsunami wave in the House, the Senate, the presidency, and in our judges.

00:19:07.764 --> 00:19:07.963
If there is voter fraud or corruption, we call for it to be exposed. We call for a free and fair election.

00:19:07.964 --> 00:19:08.063
You told me a great shaking is coming over finances, and we will be ready.

00:19:08.064 --> 00:19:08.263
You warned me about the four oak trees, Lord. You told me to get my house prepared.

00:19:08.264 --> 00:19:08.363
I thank You that You will always protect and provide for Your beloved regardless of what happens with the finances.

00:19:08.364 --> 00:19:08.463
We will have a turn of events and we will be blessed in the city and the field.

00:19:08.464 --> 00:19:08.563
Even if the house has rotten boards, we can rebuild because the foundation is built on Jesus.

00:19:08.564 --> 00:19:08.763
We took communion at Plymouth Rock. Our foundation is "In God We Trust."We put God at the forefront of our nation again.

00:19:08.764 --> 00:19:08.963
We worship You, Lord, that You are not done with America. An October surprise is not a bad thing; it’s a surprise that the glory is here.

00:19:08.964 --> 00:19:09.163
We refuse to allow terrorism. We take authority over terrorist activity.

00:19:09.164 --> 00:19:09.363
We wrestle not against flesh and blood. You will not cause any kind of demonic hindrance in our election.

00:19:09.364 --> 00:19:09.463
We call forth a supernatural exposing of darkness and an acceleration of the glory of the Lord.

00:19:09.464 --> 00:19:09.663
Peace will reign over this nation. We lift up the nation of Canada.

00:19:09.664 --> 00:19:09.863
We call for Justin Trudeau to be removed in Jesus'name. We intercede on behalf of other nations.

00:19:09.864 --> 00:19:10.063
We call for righteous indignation to rise up in Canada. We pray for Australia, England, France, all of Europe, Asia, Africa, and South Africa.

00:19:10.064 --> 00:19:10.263
There will be a great harvest and a move of the Spirit of God. We call for a spirit of boldness over the people.

00:19:10.264 --> 00:19:10.363
It will happen again: one last revival and a great harvest of souls.

00:19:10.364 --> 00:19:10.463
Father, I thank You that people will vote and not be tricked by wording regarding abortion.

00:19:10.464 --> 00:19:10.663
I call for the righteous to rise up and vote righteous. I ask the Holy Spirit to work on hearts and give them a supernatural tug of compassion.

00:19:10.664 --> 00:19:10.963
I call for the Holy Spirit to take over in the voting booth. Convict them of going the wrong way. Give them an experience with You at that voting booth.

00:19:10.964 --> 00:19:11.063
After the elections, let there be a peaceful transition of power on January 6th and January 21st.

00:19:11.064 --> 00:19:11.263
Peace that passes understanding. This has been bathed in prayer by millions.

00:19:11.264 --> 00:19:11.463
We trust You confidently. There will be life in the mother’s womb and no death.

00:19:11.464 --> 00:19:11.763
This stops now. Life will be life. We pray for the hearts of the women and their decisions.

00:19:11.764 --> 00:19:11.863
We pray for children diagnosed in the womb with learning disabilities or birth defects.

00:19:11.864 --> 00:19:12.063
We call forth wholeness in that womb. We pray for new sonograms and ultrasounds to show healing.

00:19:12.064 --> 00:19:12.263
Every child will be whole and well. This spirit of murder is bound.

00:19:12.264 --> 00:19:12.463
We call for peace in all areas. Holy Spirit, pray through us in a heavenly language.

00:19:12.464 --> 00:53:30.067
We call those things that be not as though they were. We pray over Nevada and the swing states.

00:53:30.068 --> 00:57:17.277
We call the swing states to a red wave in the name of Jesus. We believe You are able to do exceedingly abundantly above all we ask.

00:57:17.278 --> 00:58:14.021
Perfect prayers are coming out of our spirit. Every tongue that rises against us, we condemn it.

00:58:14.022 --> 00:59:27.574
Expose the darkness in Jesus'name. We have fire in our bones.

00:59:27.575 --> 01:00:26.395
We are bold about taking our land back for Jesus. I believe we received what we prayed today.

01:00:26.396 --> 01:00:50.593
If you haven't subscribed, please subscribe. We’re doing 30 days of prayer for America and the nations.

01:00:50.595 --> 01:01:23.075
Like the video and click the notification bell to help us get the videos out.

01:01:23.076 --> 01:01:37.797
