01:01:37.798 --> 01:02:05.201
What you pray forth into the spirit realm will manifest into the natural.

01:02:05.202 --> 01:02:39.679
We speak a blessing over your households, finances, jobs, raises, and bonuses.

01:02:39.680 --> 01:03:02.560
We are the head and not the tail, above and not beneath. You enlarge our territory and cause no pain. It comes to pass at last in the name of Jesus. Amen.

